QuestData.Title: Fetid Filets
QuestData.Description:
You know, it occurred to me that since this creature has been imbued with void energy, it may prefer a more... corrupted food source.
I speak, of course, of the Minions of N'Zoth.
It's a long shot, but it's worth a try.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa pieces of Corrupted Flesh from creatures in areas under assault by N'Zoth's minions.
